Class Appointments

java.lang.Object
com.michael.c195_software2.Appointments
public class Appointments extends Object
This class is the backbone of the variables within appointments. This class contains both a constructor and setters and getters. This allows the code to be extended beyond creating an entirely new appointment the dev can simply change aspects.
